front.title: •Admiral Motti
front.gametext: Deploys -2 if at least two Imperial starships on table. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Subtracts 1 from forfeit of Rebel pilots at same system.
front.lore: Senior Navy Commander of Death Star. Believes in technology. Ridiculed the Force. Ambitious leader. Promoted due to support of New Order, not military skills. Hates Vader.

combo: Admiral Motti + Lone Pilot Add two battle destiny if Motti is defending a battle alone at a system.
Admiral Motti + Vader's Eye + Lone Warrior Add two battle destiny if Motti is defending a battle alone at a site.
